description.narrative: Through UNICEF direct support, 115 schools were supported to access basic WASH facilities in schools (WinS) during the first half of 2020. WinS activities are under implementation in additional 500 schools. State ToT events were undertaken to support Three Star approach in Rakhine State in Q1. An RFP was launched to construct WASH facilities in 50 schools in conflict areas of Rakhine State. Procurement underway for WASH in School Technical Manual production. All activities were significantly delayed by COVID-19 restrictions and school closure. 15 rural healthcare facilities have been supported with improvements. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:30/07/2020
